Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman's stopovers include Oman, the United Arab Emirates, Qatar, Bahrain, and Kuwait.
Notably, this is the first visit to Qatar since Saudi Arabia and its Arab allies imposed an embargo on Qatar in mid-2017, leading to the Gulf diplomatic crisis.
